 {"id":"bd-3ar8v.2.8.3","title":"[Phase 1][Support] Fail-closed primary-outcomes claim-integrity checks in run_all gate","description":"Non-overlapping support slice for bd-3ar8v.2.8: enforce in scripts/e2e/run_all.sh that phase1_matrix_validation primary_outcomes (wall_clock_ms, rust_vs_node_ratio, rust_vs_bun_ratio, ordering_policy) are validated fail-closed when CLAIM_INTEGRITY_REQUIRED=1, and add/adjust gate tests to lock this behavior.","design":"Implement claim-integrity validation in scripts/e2e/run_all.sh for phase1_matrix_validation.primary_outcomes and emit explicit claim_integrity.* gate checks for missing/invalid wall_clock/ratios/ordering policy. Lock behavior with static gate tests in tests/ci_full_suite_gate.rs and tests/qa_docs_policy_validation.rs.","acceptance_criteria":"1) run_all validates phase1_matrix_validation.primary_outcomes fields wall_clock_ms, rust_vs_node_ratio, rust_vs_bun_ratio, ordering_policy with fail-closed behavior under CLAIM_INTEGRITY_REQUIRED. 2) New/updated claim_integrity check IDs are emitted for missing/invalid primary outcomes and invalid ordering policy. 3) ci_full_suite_gate and qa_docs_policy_validation tests assert token wiring for the new checks. 4) Targeted tests pass via rch.","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"CloudyBridge","created_at":"2026-02-16T13:39:39.386319867Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-16T14:02:14.876544759Z","closed_at":"2026-02-16T14:02:14.876498052Z","close_reason":"Completed: verified fail-closed primary_outcomes claim-integrity checks are present in run_all and gate tests; targeted rch tests passed.","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["benchmark","claim-integrity","perf-3x","phase-1","support"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3ar8v.2.8.3","depends_on_id":"bd-3ar8v.2.8","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-16T13:39:39.386319867Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
 {"id":"bd-3ar8v.2.8.4","title":"[Phase 1][Support] Enforce primary_outcomes.status validity in run_all claim-integrity gate","description":"Non-overlapping support slice under bd-3ar8v.2.8: in scripts/e2e/run_all.sh require primary_outcomes.status in phase1_matrix_validation, validate allowed values, and fail closed when invalid; update tests/ci_full_suite_gate.rs static token coverage accordingly.","notes":"Completed non-overlap claim-integrity hardening for phase1 matrix in scripts/e2e/run_all.sh + tests/ci_full_suite_gate.rs: required primary_outcomes now includes status; added fail-closed status validation check id claim_integrity.phase1_matrix_primary_outcomes_status_valid requiring pass/fail; updated remediation/required-field text; wired static token assertion in ci_full_suite_gate token list. Validation: bash -n scripts/e2e/run_all.sh (pass); rustfmt --edition 2024 --check tests/ci_full_suite_gate.rs (pass); RCH_FORCE_REMOTE=true rch exec -- env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=/data/tmp/pi_agent_rust/boldreef TMPDIR=/data/tmp/pi_agent_rust/boldreef/tmp cargo test --test ci_full_suite_gate run_all_wires_scenario_cell_status_artifacts_into_evidence_contract -- --nocapture (1 passed); RCH_FORCE_REMOTE=true rch exec -- env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=/data/tmp/pi_agent_rust/boldreef TMPDIR=/data/tmp/pi_agent_rust/boldreef/tmp cargo test --test qa_docs_policy_validation run_all_claim_integrity_python_block_compiles -- --nocapture (1 passed).","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"BoldReef","created_at":"2026-02-16T14:34:13.061417433Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-16T14:36:33.269449950Z","closed_at":"2026-02-16T14:36:33.269353230Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["claim-integrity","perf-3x","phase-1","testing"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3ar8v.2.8.4","depends_on_id":"bd-3ar8v.2.8","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-16T14:34:13.061417433Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
 {"id":"bd-3ar8v.2.8.5","title":"[Phase 1][Support] Validate matrix_cells primary_e2e metrics in run_all claim-integrity","description":"Follow-on support under bd-3ar8v.2.8: add fail-closed claim-integrity check in scripts/e2e/run_all.sh that each phase1 matrix cell carries positive primary_e2e wall_clock/rust_vs_node/rust_vs_bun metrics; wire static token coverage in tests/ci_full_suite_gate.rs.","notes":"Completed follow-on claim-integrity hardening in scripts/e2e/run_all.sh + tests/ci_full_suite_gate.rs: added fail-closed check id claim_integrity.phase1_matrix_cells_primary_e2e_metrics_present requiring positive wall_clock_ms/rust_vs_node_ratio/rust_vs_bun_ratio for each phase1 matrix cell primary_e2e payload; wired static token assertion in ci_full_suite_gate. Validation: bash -n scripts/e2e/run_all.sh (pass); rustfmt --edition 2024 --check tests/ci_full_suite_gate.rs (pass); RCH_FORCE_REMOTE=true rch exec -- env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=/data/tmp/pi_agent_rust/boldreef TMPDIR=/data/tmp/pi_agent_rust/boldreef/tmp cargo test --test ci_full_suite_gate run_all_wires_scenario_cell_status_artifacts_into_evidence_contract -- --nocapture (1 passed); RCH_FORCE_REMOTE=true rch exec -- env CARGO_TARGET_DIR=/data/tmp/pi_agent_rust/boldreef TMPDIR=/data/tmp/pi_agent_rust/boldreef/tmp cargo test --test qa_docs_policy_validation run_all_claim_integrity_python_block_compiles -- --nocapture (1 passed).","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"BoldReef","created_at":"2026-02-16T14:37:59.061047225Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-16T14:39:30.980723426Z","closed_at":"2026-02-16T14:39:30.980631394Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["claim-integrity","perf-3x","phase-1","testing"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-3ar8v.2.8.5","depends_on_id":"bd-3ar8v.2.8","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-16T14:37:59.061047225Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
